snippet.title: Best VGM 1055 - Sonic Adventure 2 - Dive Into The Mellow (Aquatic Mine)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast / Gamecube
Sonic Adventure 2 (2001)
Dive Into The Mellow (Aquatic Mine)
Tomoya Ohtani & Hunnid-P
